This was a second nighttime visit to this location. The first visit a week ago was a pre-ordered meal requested for walk-in pick-up. The order had not been processed, and it took thirty minutes, at least, to get the food. The second time I decided to forego pre-ordering, and experience the drive through. I estimate there were about ten cars ahead, and to their credit they did have a clerk out taking orders. We were able to get the order in twenty minutes. As we left and looked inside there were customers still at the inside counter,  still waiting for food, who were already there when we pulled up. This location should not do pre-orders, nor, indoor ordering after 9pm, and just focus on drive-thru, hopefully, expediting the process, or, having an on sight night manager.
